# HISTORY
# 

# A client with an Arrow Button pointing upwards should appear. 

CompareVisual ArrowButton2
Continue

# The Arrow should have turned Red and a highlight border should appear.

LocatePointer ArrowButton2
CompareVisual Shell1
Continue

# The border should be enlarged and the Arrow should point left.

CompareVisual ArrowButton2
Continue

# The shadow thickness should have increased. The Top Shadow should be 
#  pink and the Arrow should point to the right.

CompareVisual ArrowButton2
Continue

# The bottom shadow color should be green and the Arrow should point down.

CompareVisual ArrowButton2
Continue

LocatePointer ArrowButton1
ClickMB Btn1
LocatePointer ArrowButton2
ClickMB Btn1
Continue

LocatePointer ArrowButton1
ClickMB Btn1
LocatePointer ArrowButton2
ClickMB Btn1
CompareVisual parent1
Exit


